These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: martial-arts, animation, spy, sports, western, action, crime
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: country, metal, gospel, salsa, dubstep, funk, electronic
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: handball, skateboarding, biathlon, basketball, lacrosse, sailing, baseball
 1. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is baseball is between the fan of metal and the fan of country##2
 4. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the fan of metal is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 7. the fan of salsa is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person watching western movies##2
 8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 9. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
10. the person watching crime movies is the fan of gospel##1
11. the fan of funk is the person watching sports movies##1
12. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
13. the person who's sport is handball is the fan of dubstep##1
14. the person watching action movies is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is baseball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | western | martial-arts     | action | animation | sports | crime  | spy  |
| Music-Genre   | country  | salsa        | metal  | electronic     | funk   | gospel       | dubstep   |
| Sport         | skateboarding   | baseball | basketball    | biathlon  | lacrosse | sailing | handball |

