.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: pakistani, french, turkish, malaysian, russian, indonesian, italian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: skateboarding, water-polo, biathlon, rowing, lacrosse, weightlifting, baseball
The people use 7 different means of transport: subway, airplane, jet-ski, motorbike, quad-bike, van, skateboard
 1. the french is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the italian##1
 6. the pakistani is the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the pakistani is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person driving the skateboard##2
 8. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the russian##1
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
10. the turkish is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
11. the russian is on the right of the pakistani##1
12. the person driving the subway is the french##1
13. the malaysian is on the left of the pakistani##1
14. the malaysian is on the right of the person driving the van##1
15. the french is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Nationality   | indonesian | italian      | malaysian     | pakistani  | russian | turkish | french |
