 3. the german is the person watching crime movies##1
 4. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
 5. the canadian is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
 6. the person eating kiwi is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating lettuce is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the pakistani is the person watching sports movies##1
10. the canadian is the person eating mango##1
11. the person watching western movies is the brazilian##1
12. the person eating cherry is the malaysian##1
13. the british is on the far right##1
14. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching western movies and the person watching crime movies##2
15. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

