.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-16::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  engineer, doctor, paramedic, librarian, police-officer, bartender, security-guard
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: soul, classical, electronic, funk, jazz, folk, ambient
7 different pets are kept: fish, rat, lizard, turtle, frog, rabbit, cat
 1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the paramedic##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is between the fan of jazz and the fan of electronic##2
 3. the fan of soul is the owner of the rat##1
 4. the fan of ambient is on the left of the bartender##1
 5. the fan of soul is the engineer##1
 6. the paramedic is in the middle##1
 7. the police-officer is the fan of folk##1
 8. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 9. the fan of soul is the owner of the rat##1
10. the security-guard is the owner of the frog##1
11. the engineer is on the right of the librarian##1
12. the fan of ambient is on the left of the bartender##1
13. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
14. the fan of classical is on the left of the engineer##1
15. the security-guard is on the right of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2       |    3     |     4      |    5     |    6    |     7      |
| Job           | doctor | bartender | police-officer | paramedic  | security-guard   | librarian | engineer      |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | electronic        | folk    | jazz     | funk     | classical   | soul        |
| Pet           | fish   | lizard       | rabbit    | turtle | frog | cat   | rat |

