.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-17::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: rock-climbing, video-games, skydiving, puzzles, board-games, magic-tricks, card-games
7 different pets are kept: rabbit, horse, mouse, pony, bird, chinchilla, guinea-pig
The people use 7 different means of transport: van, roller, helicopter, bus, subway, skateboard, train
 1. the person driving the train is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
 2. the person driving the train is the owner of the horse##1
 3. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is the person driving the subway##1
10. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
11. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is the owner of the bird##1
13. the person driving the bus is the owner of the chinchilla##1
14. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person driving the van##1
15. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Hobby       | skydiving  | magic-tricks | puzzles  | card-games | video-games | board-games | rock-climbing |
| Pet         | pony | mouse    | rabbit        | bird      | chinchilla     | horse   | guinea-pig |
| Transport   | helicopter  | roller   | subway | skateboard        | bus    | train  | van   |

