.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-18::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: drama, fantasy, western, scientific, sports, mystery, comedy
7 different pets are kept: bird, rat, lizard, cat, dog, chinchilla, goat
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: water-polo, parkour, handball, lacrosse, rugby, tennis, badminton
 1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is in the middle##1
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 8. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 9. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching sports movies and the person who's sport is rugby##2
10. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
11. the person watching fantasy movies is the owner of the cat##1
12. the person watching mystery movies is in the middle##1
13. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
14. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
15. the person who's sport is handball is the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |     7      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy   | fantasy    | sports  | mystery        | drama | western | scientific     |
| Pet           | rat | cat | goat     | chinchilla      | dog     | bird     | lizard    |
| Sport         | water-polo   | tennis  | handball | parkour | rugby    | lacrosse  | badminton |

