.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-19::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  project-manager, social-worker, doctor, analyst, software-developer, writer, designer
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: scientific, western, fantasy, martial-arts, superhero, spy, adventure
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: lacrosse, basketball, water-polo, sailing, tennis, climbing, skateboarding
 1. the analyst is on the left of the designer##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 4. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 5. the writer is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 6. the designer is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person watching martial-arts movies is in the middle##1
10. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
11. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the social-worker##1
12. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the doctor and the person who's sport is climbing##2
13. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
14. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's sport is climbing##1
15. the project-manager is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |      4      |      5       |      6      |      7       |
| Job           | doctor      | project-manager | software-developer | social-worker   | writer | analyst | designer |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | fantasy   | scientific   | martial-arts | western        | superhero       | spy       |
| Sport         | basketball    | lacrosse       | climbing   | sailing      | skateboarding   | water-polo  | tennis |

