.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-20::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, water, lemonade, hot-chocolate, mirinda, soy-milk, tea
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, woodworking, video-games, puzzles, fishing, rock-climbing, card-games
7 different pets are kept: turtle, fish, chinchilla, horse, rabbit, bird, rat
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 2. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1
 3. the person drinking water is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the person drinking tea is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the bird is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 8. the owner of the horse is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 9. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
10. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in the middle##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
13. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
14. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the owner of the rat and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
15. the owner of the rat is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5      |      6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | tea  | soy-milk   | mirinda   | hot-chocolate        | lemonade     | water | milk       |
| Hobby      | board-games | woodworking | card-games | puzzles | video-games  | fishing   | rock-climbing |
| Pet        | rat   | fish     | turtle     | bird      | rabbit | horse    | chinchilla      |

 